					<h1 class="entry-title">School Closure Extended</h1>

					<div class="entry-meta">
						<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://shenango.k12.pa.us/school-closure-extended-2/" title="10:08 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">April 9, 2020</span></a> <span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://shenango.k12.pa.us/author/rheath/" title="View all posts by Rob Heath">Rob Heath</a></span>					</div>
<!-- .entry-meta -->

					<div class="entry-content">
						<p>This morning, Governor Wolf closed public schools for the remainder of the 2019-2020 academic school year.  To continue helping students move forward academically, we will continue to provide remote learning for all of our students K-12.  Please encourage your child to complete all assigned work and to reach out to their teachers or building administration if there are questions or concerns.</p>
<p>We will provide information about remaining spring activities the near future. Please stay safe and healthy.<br>
#Wildcatstrong</p>
